      A info text strings must contain: CANAME, CERT_SUBJECTDN, EXT_ABBR_SUBJECTALTNAME, CATYPE, EXPIRES, STATUS, DESCRIPTION, CRL_CA_CRLPERIOD, CRL_CA_ISSUEINTERVAL, CRL_CA_OVERLAPTIME, CRL_CA_DELTACRLPERIOD, PUBLISHERS, VALIDATORS It must also have CADATA in position n° 4 (CA data) It must also have CRLSPECIFICDATA in position n° 9 (CRL Specific Data) It must also have SERVICES in position n° 15 (Services), if exists
